  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Take 500 Needy Children In Somalia to School</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Somalia National military forces and armed militia such as the Al Shaabab militia recruit children for many reasons. Children especially boys are recruited as fighters, messengers, spies, checkpoint controllers, to conduct suicide attacks, assassinations and in assembling and planting of improvised explosive devices (IEDs) whereas girls are recruited as cooks, cleaners and are sometimes forcedly married by the armed forces and groups. This project envisage to take 500 needy children to school.</narrative>
  </description>
